The Conjuring;;83;;86;;R;;In 1970, paranormal investigators and demonologists Lorraine (Vera Farmiga) and Ed (Patrick Wilson) Warren are summoned to the home of Carolyn (Lili Taylor) and Roger (Ron Livingston) Perron. The Perrons and their five daughters have recently moved into a secluded farmhouse, where a supernatural presence has made itself known. Though the manifestations are relatively benign at first, events soon escalate in horrifying fashion, especially after the Warrens discover the house's macabre history.;;Mystery & thriller,Horror;;James Wan;;2013;;Vera Farmiga,Patrick Wilson,Lili Taylor,Ron Livingston,Shanley Caswell,Hayley McFarland,Joey King,Mackenzie Foy,Kyla Deaver,Shannon Kook,John Brotherton,Sterling Jerins,Marion Guyot,Morganna Bridgers,Amy Tipton,Steve Coulter;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_conjuring